			<header class="entry-header">

				<h1 class="entry-title" itemprop="name">La France veut se mettre à l&#039;abri du cyber-terrorisme</h1>

				<div class="entry-author-date">
					<span class="author vcard">Olivier Robillart</span>, <span class="date"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2008-07-11T10:11:25+02:00" itemprop="datePublished">11 juillet 2008, 10:11</time></span>				</div>
								<div itemprop="breadcrumb" class="entry-breadcrumb"><a href="https://www.silicon.fr/actualites/security" title="View all posts in Sécurité">Sécurité</a></div>				<div class="entry-tools"></div>

			</header>
